{"tid":2246701,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新加坡增3宗確診 受旅遊氣泡影響星港來回機票漲4成","createTime":"2020-10-17T09:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T10:26:07.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7128f3334f2ccb8cf33e3cb3cba81763354f96ed","tid":2246701,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T09:33:42.000Z","msg":"新加坡增3宗確診 星港來回機票漲4成<br />\n<br />\n即將同香港建立航空旅遊氣泡的新加坡，今日新增3宗新型冠狀病毒確診病例，其中2宗是本地病例，1宗是社區感染，另1宗是外勞宿舍。<br />\n<br />\n星港前日宣布準備建立航空旅遊氣泡後，新加坡往返香港的機票價格上漲4成。新加坡航空公司網站顯示，從現時到年底最便宜來回香港的經濟艙機票，昨晚加到558坡元，折合約3200港元，比前日的400坡元高。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2362059\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2362059&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=3b5eec86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2362059</a>"},{"pid":"5ac1e27ed9c1e07c85315ac748df69cb08fd04ca","tid":2246701,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:04:17.000Z","msg":"Monkeypore ? 不了"},{"pid":"3029dd66adb4b13b9724b3a5dd280312becce68d","tid":2246701,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:08:08.000Z","msg":"去新加坡本身好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca59ee24ecdc4d1d7f219baf24b4da3a1aa85c1e","tid":2246701,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:26:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}